Name: Flamer Baron
Difficulty: Medium/hard
Connection: Baron of Hell
Summon: FlamerBaron
Melee: yes
Distance: Projectile
Type: Demon
Brightmaps: No
Actor modification: Yes
ACS: No


A Baron of Hell modified to also spray you with green hellfire if you get too close. He'll still use the normal green fireball attack as well.

Tested in (G)ZDoom.
